Structure:
`dev' : general documentation files
`dev/modules': documentation for modules


In order to modify the documentation,
the following packages should already be installed:
1. asciidoctor
2. pygments.rb


Update general uDeviceX tools if necessary:
1. cd ..
2. make install


After modifying existing files:
1. make
2. ./tools/start -> starts server. do it only once
3. ./tools/view -> to view changes locally
4. add/commit/push to udx repo
5. ./tools/deploy -> updates online documentation [ssh key in github account must me set!]

If NEW files are added:
 run ./configure and follow the procedure for modifying files
